{"tid":1373803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"引戰","createTime":"2019-07-27T16:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T18:49:03.000Z","uid":92908,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3c5900d42adaf8e0bba2b2bd94ce8aec0ebbf237","tid":1373803,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:19:58.000Z","msg":"要打一定要天光打，入夜人少左，和班非又趕番屋企，一定唔好硬守到夜晚，大家都清楚夜晚人一定少，又一定危險性高左，狗仔調兵又快左<br />\n<br />\n要果要贏，要天光就引戰，次次對峙到夜晚d狗就開始發難<br />\n<br />\n前線又屌和理非太早走，和理非又屌前線死留太夜<br />\n<br />\n點解唔好似612、上水咁，天光打，對我地有利好多<br />\n<br />\n人數係我地既優勢，不如就係我地最有優勢既時候引戰，而最易引戰就係掉雜物"},{"pid":"6180234f1ab82c1a7dac09127bc505c78f22ce92","tid":1373803,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:23:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"350f669ff60a87612cda8f60b2893aa3346cec0b","tid":1373803,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:23:19.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"7278b8f6a6b7d3b0479570f33a8c7679bcbec6b0","tid":1373803,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:23:33.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"1e843bb0010ab78a340f2115c0b780969c079d2d","tid":1373803,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:23:44.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"728c91622b3cf5c29b08abad3297f1ff011f3d57","tid":1373803,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:23:55.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"b57ebdb3a7322565f893015ee50e0a95c70076e7","tid":1373803,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:24:06.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"77402fbba53948f73e9099224bfd78dd4a980c23","tid":1373803,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:24:18.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"7b11b8696c342f9f1b7537d4080e0adf4e1cc87e","tid":1373803,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:24:28.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"d116addd665787c69aa5a54fcdda743145f47c23","tid":13