n style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">知</span></span>"},{"pid":"7db4ef5e12f68c0b0e5a8418c75d707230984719","tid":1373803,"uid":186509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:29:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4907e76a838e8a7492fe10a646068b26e6569039","tid":1373803,"uid":140326,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:29:29.000Z","msg":"勇武決定左要留，已經做好比攻擊準備，<br />\n真正留喺現場嘅勇武兄弟，<br />\n係唔會怪自已人離開，<br />\n即使離開現場，<br />\n和理非心中都會支持留守兄弟決定，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">留下：支持；離開：專重</span></span><br />\n有班3毛扮勇武屌自己人散水，<br />\n和理非唔好被影響到<br />\n<br />\n勇武其實已經有左付死嘅決心，<br />\n死都唔怕，點會怕比人拉同比人打，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武在乎嘅係用自己嘅生命去揭露政權嘅邪惡，</span></span><br />\n我地應該給予最大專重同支持，<br />\n留低嘅人就盡量留到最後，<br />\n直至政府宣布特赦呢班義士為止<br />\n<br />\n【散水】有份叫人730走嘅入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1373646\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1373646</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7e888d5950a0ddd3a4977fddb0e1496d1dbaa2aa","tid":1373803,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:30:24.000Z","msg":"冇錯，每一次天一黑冇咁多記者影到就會開始亂鳩咁嚟"},{"pid":"da99663df73c336b302d86b2dee01076259f2add","tid":1373803,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e888d5950a0ddd3a4977fddb0e1496d1dbaa2aa","tid":1373803,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:30:24.000Z","msg":"冇錯，每一次天一黑冇咁多記者影到就會開始亂鳩咁嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:30:57.000Z","msg":"最緊要係連和理非都多"},{"pid":"abc6307ea663db6708bea9458fda4941ba9d3aa8","tid":1373803,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:33:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50a0243024eddf38abd86e6f251a18e9e8bd26e4","tid":1373803,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:58:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39db0e88053e108a4694455ce83ab3344e4bf20c","tid